WORLD BEATERS 
The United States won the Golf World Cup after a final round of 67 was enough for Matt Kuchar and Gary Woodland to capture the title by two strokes from Germany and England. 
 USA claim the World Cup! 
 
   
 
 
 

 


  
  
 
 
     
 
 
 
 
